5. MODDING POLICY
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Create Your Adventure supports and encourages community creativity through
mods and texture packs, subject to the following terms:

5.1 WHAT IS PERMITTED

  - Creating gameplay modifications ("Mods") that alter or extend
    the behavior of the game.
  - Creating texture packs that replace or modify the visual assets of the game.
  - Sharing and distributing Mods and Texture Packs freely within the community.

5.2 INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY OF MODS

  - The original code and assets created by a Mod author remain the
    intellectual property of that Mod author.
  - However, all Mods and Texture Packs are considered dependent works,
    as they cannot function without Create Your Adventure.
  - Oliver Schmidt retains the right to determine whether Mods are
    permitted within the CyA ecosystem.

5.3 WHAT IS NOT PERMITTED

  - Selling Mods or Texture Packs for monetary gain in any form,
    including but not limited to: direct sales, donations tied to
    exclusive content, subscription models, or paywalls.
  - Using Mods or Texture Packs for any commercial purpose without
    the explicit written permission of Oliver Schmidt.
  - Distributing Mods that contain malicious code, exploit game systems
    in harmful ways, or violate any applicable law.

5.4 GOVERNING LAW FOR MODDERS

  This Modding Policy is governed by the laws of the Federal Republic
  of Germany, regardless of the Mod author's country of residence.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
6. PURCHASE & OWNERSHIP
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

6.1 ONE-TIME PURCHASE

  Create Your Adventure is sold under a one-time purchase model.
  Once purchased, the player owns their copy of the game indefinitely,
  with no subscriptions, recurring fees, or forced online activation.
  This reflects the philosophy of classic game ownership – you buy it,
  you own it, forever.

6.2 EXPANSIONS

  CyA may offer optional Expansions (e.g. technology-themed content,
  castle building, RPG elements) that extend the base game experience.
  These Expansions:

  - Are installed automatically alongside the base game.
  - Can be individually enabled or disabled by the player at any time.
  - Are each subject to a separate one-time purchase if applicable.
  - Will never be required to enjoy the base game experience.

6.3 NO MICROTRANSACTIONS

  Create Your Adventure will never contain microtransactions, loot boxes,
  pay-to-win mechanics, or any other form of predatory monetization.
  All content is fairly priced and clearly communicated upfront.

6.4 RESALE & SHARING

  Purchased copies of the game may not be resold or transferred to
  another person without explicit written permission from Oliver Schmidt.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
7. SUCCESSION & DEATH CLAUSE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

In the event of the death of Oliver Schmidt, the following terms apply:

  - All rights, ownership, and intellectual property of Create Your Adventure
    and its source code shall immediately and automatically transfer to the
    public domain.
  - The Software shall become fully Open Source upon confirmation of
    Oliver Schmidt's passing, free for anyone to use, modify, and distribute.
  - No individual, company, or legal entity may claim ownership over
    the Software following this transition.

This clause reflects the author's wish that Create Your Adventure continues
to live on and benefit the community, regardless of personal circumstances.

